Last week, medium concentration was reported in Pinellas County and its coastal zone, low to high concentration in Hillsborough County coastal zone, high concentration in Manat County, high concentration in Sarasota County and its coastal zone, average concentration in Charlotte County, high concentration in Lee County and its coastal areas as well.
